Heritage Images Photo Prints and Wall Art

Napoleon Bidding Farewell to Marshal Jean Lannes, 1858. Artist: Dorian

Napoleon Bidding Farewell to Marshal Jean Lannes, 1858. The Emperor Napoleon (1769-1821) with Marshal Lannes (1769-1809) after the latter suffered a mortal wound at the Battle of Aspern-Essling in Austria on 22 May 1809. Found in the collection of the State Borodino War and History Museum, Moscow. Heritage Images features heritage image collections. Â© Fine Art Images
